🧠 GS-Level Answer

👉 “When would you use Pandas?”

💬 Strong Answer:

“I use Pandas for in-memory data processing where we need fast filtering, aggregation, and transformation of structured data. It is especially useful for analytics, batch processing, and prototyping data pipelines. For large-scale distributed systems, I would switch to tools like Spark.”

